 retailers learn how ecommerce companies think” zhang also believes that china’s business model is better suited to emerging markets and is therefore bringing that model to developing nations in asia in indonesia hillhouse launched a joint venture between mobile messaging platform wechat and indonesia’s giant communications and media conglomerate global mediacom “indonesia is now like china some years ago” commented zhang sender also explains that zhang’s investment philosophy is comparable to that of warren buffett which is to buy and hold “in a world of speculators zhang’s philosophy stands out” insider monkey pointed out that some of hillhouse’s investment decisions could be classified as contrarian although they do maintain a considerable number of mainstream investments as well notable investorsedit under a plan reported in august  for stanford university to invest about  million with hillhouse the group will be investing money for at least six of the  wealthiest universities in the us referencesedit  a b c d e f sender henny  june  zhang lei has lunch with the ft financial times retrieved  march    nadeem m  january  hillhouse capital management cuts passive stake insider monkey retrieved  march    a b c lowprofile beijing fund with envious record subscription only ftcom january   partially retrieved   a b hu bei  january  hillhouse capital said to raise  billion private equity fund bloomberg business retrieved  march    investment philosophy hillhouse capital retrieved  march    value investing congress retrieved  march    sender henny  june  zhang lei has lunch with the ft financial times retrieved  april  the fund is named after an avenue in new haven that’s a block from where the yale investment office used to be located   mcenery thornton the  biggest asianbased hedge funds businessinsidercom may   retrieved   zhangvalueinvestingcongresswestpdfdead link valuewalkcom   research  rankings top of the hill institutional investors alphacenveomobilecom summer  